name: All Eyes On You
description:
Can you see it?

They look at you, all of them. Maybe they don’t have pair of eyes like us, but they have a sight like ours. 

Like us, plants respond to light. Just as we have photoreceptors in our eyes, plants also have theirs across their stems and leaves.
 Take a look at this picture, I bet you can feel it .. Can you feel that they can see you too?
 
Yes, you’re the light.

Shot on Minolta Mac Tele/Kodak Colorplus 200 | C41 Process | Fuji Frontier Scan | 3602 × 2397px
